{"tid":1091863,"cid":23,"subCid":0,"title":"部老爺機睇尼仲頂到幾年。。。","createTime":"2019-04-04T11:51:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-05T07:39:19.000Z","uid":191921,"like":4,"dislike":21,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"5c8b156eb1a9cb469379437e9d19e8ca3a402e43","tid":1091863,"uid":191921,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-04T11:51:44.000Z","msg":"話說部800e 上網睇人review就出名高iso 廢，的確係，影jpeg 衰過m43, 但轉一轉影raw 呢：<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TBtjSoU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTBtjSoU.jpg&h=efc02e15&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n極限iso 原生 6400，都叫做見得人，仔細度拍得住z7 新機，當然代價係彩噪大粒過人地<br />\n<br />\n再試埋極限25600, 嘩屌，噪點彈珠咁款，點撚用？<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Ohg5NYv.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOhg5NYv.jpg&h=2729c41c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n但細節度同對比其實仲好似好過新機。。。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">機係死，人就生ge, 研究左好耐終於有計搞noise！！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n結果以下呢幾張用左25600最高 iso 影。。。純試機相，唔好要求幾靚<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/s5tLNZx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fs5tLNZx.jpg&h=3a423b07&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Z0tsgSU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZ0tsgSU.jpg&h=82555990&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hZ9i7ZA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhZ9i7ZA.jpg&h=f3924062&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n256k iso 尼講，我個人收哂貨了。<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">有無老爺機用家一齊分享下點樣榨盡部機的功能同研究下有咩秘技？</span></span>"},{"pid":"7f4c9f075018f0bda08a1c5dc1e3741cd2194751","tid":1091863,"uid":21423,"like":12,"dislike":3,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-04T11:54:03.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"70080e0a708f076beb8f8a9676db7a4d0c6d5636","tid":1091863,"uid":235475,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"re